{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyLayout"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyLayout\/sizeThatFits(proposal:subviews:cache:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sizeThatFits","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"proposal","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ProposedViewSize","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore16ProposedViewSizeV","text":"ProposedViewSize","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"subviews","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyLayout","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnyLayoutV","text":"AnyLayout","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":".","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Layout\/Subviews","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore6LayoutP8Subviewsa","text":"Subviews","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"cache","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"inout","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyLayout","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnyLayoutV","text":"AnyLayout","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":".","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyLayout\/Cache","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnyLayoutV5CacheV","text":"Cache","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CGSize","text":"CGSize","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A size proposal for the container. The container’s parent","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view that calls this method might call the method more than once","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with different proposals to learn more about the container’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"flexibility before deciding which proposal to use for placement.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"proposal"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A collection of proxies that represent the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"views that the container arranges. You can use the proxies in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"collection to get information about the subviews as you determine"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"how much space the container needs to display them."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"subviews"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Optional storage for calculated data that you can share among","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the methods of your custom layout container. See","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyLayout\/makeCache(subviews:)","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" for details.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"cache"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Return Value","type":"heading","anchor":"return-value","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A size that indicates how much space the container","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"needs to arrange its subviews.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Implement this method to tell your custom layout container’s parent","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view how much space the container needs for a set of subviews, given","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a size proposal. The parent might call this method more than once","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"during a layout pass with different proposed sizes to test the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"flexibility of the container, using proposals like:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ProposedViewSize\/zero","isActive":true},{"text":" proposal; respond with the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"layout’s minimum size.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ProposedViewSize\/infinity"},{"type":"text","text":" proposal; respond with the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layout’s maximum size."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ProposedViewSize\/unspecified","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" proposal; respond with the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"layout’s ideal size.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The parent might also choose to test flexibility in one dimension at a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"time. For example, a horizontal stack might propose a fixed height and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"an infinite width, and then the same height with a zero width.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following example calculates the size for a basic vertical stack"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that places views in a column, with no spacing between the views:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["private struct BasicVStack: Layout {","    func sizeThatFits(","        proposal: ProposedViewSize,","        subviews: Subviews,","        cache: inout ()","    ) -> CGSize {","        subviews.reduce(CGSize.zero) { result, subview in","            let size = subview.sizeThatFits(.unspecified)","            return CGSize(","                width: max(result.width, size.width),","                height: result.height + size.height)","        }","    }","","    \/\/ This layout also needs a placeSubviews() implementation.","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The implementation asks each subview for its ideal size by calling the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/LayoutSubview\/sizeThatFits(_:)","isActive":true},{"text":" method with an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ProposedViewSize\/unspecified","isActive":true},{"text":" proposed size.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It then reduces these values into a single size that represents","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the maximum subview width and the sum of subview heights.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because this example isn’t flexible, it ignores its size proposal","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"input and always returns the same value for a given set of subviews.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OpenSwiftUI views choose their own size, so the layout engine always","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"uses a value that you return from this method as the actual size of the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"composite view. That size factors into the construction of the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"bounds"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"input to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AnyLayout\/placeSubviews(in:proposal:subviews:cache:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Returns the size of the composite view, given a proposed size","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and the view’s subviews.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/anylayout\/sizethatfits(proposal:subviews:cache:)"]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Layout\/AnyLayout.swift#L277","fileName":"AnyLayout.swift"},"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnyLayoutV12sizeThatFits8proposal8subviews5cacheSo6CGSizeVAA16ProposedViewSizeV_AA0E8SubviewsVAC5CacheVztF","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sizeThatFits"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"proposal"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ProposedViewSize","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore16ProposedViewSizeV"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"subviews"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"AnyLayout","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnyLayoutV"},{"kind":"text","text":"."},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Subviews","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore6LayoutP8Subviewsa"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cache"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"inout"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"AnyLayout","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore9AnyLayoutV"},{"kind":"